    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sec1_note",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 310,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 66,
      "text": "Single core walks every (doc × code) index entry, dedups\nby RecordId → work ∝ amplification, not the answer.\nHeavy user (many codes, dense docs) → p99 latency spike.",
