    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sec2_note",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 576,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 40,
      "text": "Boundaries shared by neighbours (B_i = exclusive top of R_i  =  inclusive bottom of R_i+1) → ranges tile the space with no gap, no overlap.\nEvery doc lands in exactly one range → the sum of partial counts is EXACT, whatever the distribution.   MongoDBUtil.objectIdRangeBounds(4) → [B1, B2, B3]",
      "originalText": "Boundaries shared by neighbours (B_i = exclusive top of R_i  =  inclusive bottom of R_i+1) → ranges tile the space with no gap, no overlap.\nEvery doc lands in exactly one range → the sum of partial counts is EXACT, whatever the distribution.   MongoDBUtil.objectIdRangeBounds(4) → [B1, B2, B3]",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#64748b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
